cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and parsing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses a stack-LSTM model for parsing. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves designing a parsing system that combines bottom-up and top-down strategies. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for parsing. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves designing a system for recognizing patterns in syntactic trees.
